{"article_id":"3UA5GawOrAtJVhrj","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump is heading to Puerto Rico Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"to survey the devastation from Hurricane Maria","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"after he attacked San Juan 's mayor and others","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"for criticizing the federal response to the disaster .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"First lady Melania Trump will accompany President Trump on the trip ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"which comes","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"as the White House has been scrambling to show","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"it is on top of the crisis .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Nearly two weeks after the Category 4 hurricane ravaged the island ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"the situation in Puerto Rico is still unfolding :","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Some 55 percent of the 3.4 million residents are still without access to drinking water ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"and only 5 percent of the power grid has been restored .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"\" We ' re going to be seeing all of the first responders , the military , [ the Federal Emergency Management Agency ] ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"and frankly , most importantly , we ' re going to be seeing the people of Puerto Rico , \"","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Trump said Monday .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"\" It ' s been amazing what ' s been done , in a very short period of time , in Puerto Rico . \"","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"while conditions in the disaster zone have been slowly improving ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"there are still numerous roadblocks","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"hampering federal relief efforts ,","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"including destroyed roads and bridges , a lack of telecommunications and a shortage of truck drivers .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"All eyes will be on","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"when Trump comes face to face with San Juan Mayor Carmen Yulín Cruz","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"after they both publicly criticized each other 's responses to the storms .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"White House press secretary Sarah Huckabee Sanders said Monday night","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"that Cruz plans to attend a briefing","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"that Trump and the first lady will be receiving on recovery and response efforts","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"\" Our focus is to bring the mayor into the coordination efforts , \"","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Sanders said .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"\" We hope","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"that she will join with us in those efforts ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"and be part of things","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"she ' s been invited to participate in . ...","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"We hope","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"that those conversations happen","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"and we can all work together","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"to move forward . \"","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Trump ' s visit comes","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"days after Cruz criticized the hurricane response efforts","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"and made an emotional plea for someone","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"to take charge of emergency relief operations ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"heightening the sense of urgency on the island .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"\" I will do what I never thought","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"I was going to do :","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"I am begging ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"begging anyone","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"that can hear us","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"to save us from dying , \"","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Cruz said Friday afternoon .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"\" If anybody out there is listening to us ,","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"we are dying","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"and you are killing us with the inefficiency . \"","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Trump lashed out at Cruz in a series of tweets on Saturday morning ,","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"slamming her leadership","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"and suggesting","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"that her comments were politically motivated .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"\" The mayor of San Juan ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"who was very complimentary only a few days ago ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"has now been told by the Democrats","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"that you must be nasty to Trump , \"","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"`` Such poor leadership ability by the mayor of San Juan , and others in Puerto Rico ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"who are not able to get their workers to help . \"","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"The Mayor of San Juan ,","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"who was very complimentary only a few days ago ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"has now been told by the Democrats","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"that you must be nasty to Trump .","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"September 30 , 2017 ...","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Such poor leadership ability by the Mayor of San Juan , and others in Puerto Rico ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"who are not able to get their workers to help .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"They ....","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"September 30 , 2017 ...","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"want everything to be done for them","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"when it should be a community effort .","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"10,000 Federal workers now on Island","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"doing a fantastic job .","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"September 30 , 2017","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"When pressed on whether she would be willing to meet with Trump","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"following his attacks on Twitter ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"Cruz said","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"\" of course. \"","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"She emphasized","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"that the goal right now is to save lives","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"and that everything else ,","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"including \" petty comments , \"","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"are just a distraction .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"\" If he asks to meet with me ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"of course I will meet with him , ''","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"Cruz said Sunday on ABC 's `` This Week. \"","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"`` Any dialogue","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"that goes on","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"just has to be able to produce results . \"","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"`` And all","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"I did last week , or even this week ,","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"was ask for help , \"","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"she added .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"Trump ' s angry tweets over the weekend also included complaints","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"that the media was unfairly covering the hurricane devastation","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"and a suggestion","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"that Puerto Ricans want \" everything done for them \"","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"when it comes to relief efforts .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"The comments sparked widespread condemnation from Democratic lawmakers and Puerto Rican officials .","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"But the president could strike a more unifying tone","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"as he meets with storm survivors and first responders on the U.S. island territory .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"\" I expect the focus to be on the recovery efforts , \"","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"said Sanders ,","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"when pressed on whether there would be any tensions during Trump ' s visit .","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"However , Trump has waded into other sticky issues","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"when talking about the Puerto Rico crisis over the past week .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"Trump ' s first tweets last Monday pointed out","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"that the territory \" was already suffering from broken infrastructure & massive debt \"","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"and that billions of dollars are \" owed to Wall Street and the banks","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"which , sadly , must be dealt with . \"","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"Trump also suggested during a speech last week","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"that the government of Puerto Rico \" will have to work with us \"","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"to determine how the rebuilding process will be funded .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"The comments have fueled criticism","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"that the White House is treating the island territory differently than states","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"hit by hurricanes .","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"Trump ' s interactions on the ground during the roughly five-hour visit will present an opportunity","depth":6},{"id":126,"text":"for the president to play the role of comforter in chief .","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"After an initial briefing , the president and first lady are expected to visit `` individuals","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"impacted by Hurricane Maria . ''","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"The president is then scheduled to meet with Puerto Rico Gov . Ricardo Rosselló and U.S. Virgin Islands Gov . Kenneth Mapp for a `` briefing with senior military personnel . \"","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"Trump faced criticism over his first trip to Texas after Hurricane Harvey","depth":5},{"id":131,"text":"for not visiting local shelters ,","depth":6},{"id":132,"text":"meeting with victims","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"or touring significant damage .","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"The president also made headlines during that visit","depth":6},{"id":135,"text":"for praising the crowd size","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"that formed outside a Corpus Christi firehouse ,","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"while Melania Trump stirred a debate on social media","depth":6},{"id":138,"text":"for wearing stilettos heels","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"before she boarded a plane","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"headed for the disaster zone .","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"During his second visit to Texas , Trump passed out food and other supplies","depth":4},{"id":142,"text":"as he comforted Harvey survivors ,","depth":5},{"id":143,"text":"which received a warmer response .","depth":5},{"id":144,"text":"After facing days of public outcry ,","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"the White House agreed last week to temporarily lift the Jones Act ,","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"allowing foreign ships to deliver emergency aid and other supplies to Puerto Rico .","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"The 10-day waiver from the shipping law ,","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"which only allows American-made and -operated ships to deliver cargo between U.S. ports ,","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"expires on Saturday .","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"A weeklong exemption was granted for Texas and Florida after Hurricanes Harvey and Irma ,","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"and the administration extended the waiver for one additional week .","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"Lawmakers are pressing the White House to extend the waiver for Puerto Rico ,","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"pointing out","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"that the island could be rebuilding for months .","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"The topic could come up","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"as Trump meets with Puerto Rican officials and others on the ground","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"who have long championed to fully repeal the law .","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"But getting shipments to the island is only one challenge .","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"There has also been major hurdles","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"getting emergency aid and other supplies distributed ,","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"which led to a pile up of containers at the ports last week .","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"There could be reluctance to extend the waiver over concerns","depth":7},{"id":163,"text":"it could further exacerbate the problem .","depth":7},{"id":164,"text":"Lawmakers in both parties have called the White House ' s response to the crisis lacking .","depth":7},{"id":165,"text":"Members of Congress questioned","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"why Trump took eight days to waive the Jones Act","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"and deploy a three-star general","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"to coordinate distribution and relief efforts on the ground .","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"It ' s unclear whether Trump ' s trip , and the administration ' s stepped up response efforts , will be enough","depth":7},{"id":170,"text":"to mute the criticism","depth":8},{"id":171,"text":"- especially from Democrats .","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"Congress will also soon be tasked with passing a multibillion dollar disaster aid package for Puerto Rico ,","depth":6},{"id":173,"text":"and many lawmakers are eager to keep the issue in the spotlight .","depth":6},{"id":174,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Charles Schumer","depth":4},{"id":175,"text":"Charles","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"( Chuck ) Ellis Schumer","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"ivided Supreme Court leans toward allowing Trump to end DACA","depth":7},{"id":178,"text":"lhan Omar blasts Pete King as an 'Islamophobe '","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"fter he announces retirement :","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"Good riddance '","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"op Senate Dem :","depth":8},{"id":182,"text":"fficials timed immigration policy around 2020 election MORE","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"D-N.Y. )","depth":7},{"id":184,"text":"owed Monday","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"hat the mass shooting in Las Vegas Sunday night wouldn ' t distract Washington policymakers from the relief needs in the islands .","depth":8},{"id":186,"text":"Our friends and relatives and fellow Americans in Puerto Rico and the U.S. Virgin Islands should know","depth":8},{"id":187,"text":"hat","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"ven while we mourn and process the incomprehensible events in Las Vegas ,","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"e remain laser-focused on the needs of Puerto Rico and the Virgin Islands ,","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"nd will continue our advocacy for a more comprehensive , more sure-footed , and better coordinated response to their crisis , \"","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"e said .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":383,"left":321,"right":382,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":321,"left":228,"right":320,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":228,"left":212,"right":227,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":199,"right":211,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":195,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":0,"right":194,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":1,"right":193,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":196,"right":197,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":211,"left":202,"right":210,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":200,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":201,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":210,"left":204,"right":209,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":203,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":209,